name: Evolve S&P 500Â® Enhanced Yield Fund
longDescription: The fund invests primarily in the equity constituents of the S&P 500 Index, or any successor thereto, while writing covered call options on up to 33% of the portfolio, at the discretion of the Manager.  The fund seeks to provide longterm capital growth by replicating, net of fees and expenses, the performance of the SP 5 Index, or any successor thereto, while mitigating downside risk.
